'''Arcade Assogba,''' ni umukinnyi wa firime muri [[Bene]] . <ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=16738</ref> <ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.arcade-assogba.16738.html</ref> Yagize uruhare runini muri sinema ya Bénin atanga amahugurwa menshi yo gutumanaho hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga mu birori bitandukanye by’umuco <ref>https://lanationbenin.info/arcade-assogba-realisateur-letat-est-en-retard-sur-le-cinema-beninois/</ref> muri Bénin nko mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Ouidah ndetse n’ibirori mpuzamahanga bya [[Bene|Benin]], Fitheb. <ref name="filmfreeway">https://filmfreeway.com/ArcadeASSOGBA  </ref> Azwiho kandi kuba umuyobozi wa firime ngufi, ''ZanKlan''<ref>https://kitikilifilms.com/index.php/actualite/entretien-avec-arcade-assogba-a-propos-de-son-film-zanklan/</ref> .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Kuva mu 2006 kugeza 2009, Assogba yize sinema muri Institut Cinématographique de Ouidah (ICO). Nyuma yakuye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bumenyi bw’abantu n’imibereho yakuye muri kaminuza ya Paris 1 Pantheon Sorbonne naho impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu by'amategeko yakuye muri kaminuza ya Abomey-Calavi muri Bénin. <ref>http://www.cjcinema.org/pages/fiche_auteur.php?auteur=1265</ref><ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Arcade_Assogba</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Assogba yatangiye umwuga wa sinema nkumuyobozi wungirije wa mbere kuri firime nyinshi zerekanwe muri Benin. Yakoranye n'abayobozi mpuzamahanga bazwi nka Sylvestre Amoussou, Jean Odoutan, [[Pablo César (director)|Pablo César]] na Heidi Specogna na Pascale Obolo muri firime nyinshi. Muri 2018, yerekanwe bwa mbere mubuyobozi hamwe na documentaire ''Crossing.'' ''.'' ''.'' . Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa firime, yakoze Short ''ZanKlan'' mumwaka umwe. Muri make yakiriwe neza nabanegura kandi yerekanwa kandi atsindira ibihembo mubirori byinshi bya firime. Muri 2019, film yatsindiye igihembo cya 2 cyiza muri Rebiap festival international de film, Benin.<ref>https://www.agencebeninpresse.info/web/depeche/16/le-film-suru-de-kismath-baguidi-enleve-le-1er-prix-des-rebiap-2019</ref> <ref name="filmfreeway">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://filmfreeway.com/ArcadeASSOGBA "Arcade ASSOGBA: Director / Writer / 1st AD"]. filmfreeway<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref><ref>https://lamarcherepublicaine.com/index.php/culture/338-entretien-avec-le-laureat-arcade-assogba-je-suis-heureux-que-des-aines-et-pas-des-moindres-me-reconnaissent-un-merite</ref>

